# Privacy — never commit real personal health data to a public fork.
# Meal-plan templates (dietary *structure*) are fine to track; daily health/project
# status files contain personal detail and shouldn't live in a public repo.
#
# In this private repo we KEEP them tracked for the app to load.
# If you fork this repo publicly, uncomment the next two lines:
#
#   health-daily/
#   project-status/

# Backup/intermediate files
*.bak
*.tmp
.DS_Store
